                                        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Get notified for the crowdfunding!</h2>
                                        <p class="mx-auto mt-2 max-w-xl text-center text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">When we'll launch the Crowdfunding on Kickstarter you'll receive an email about it!</p>
